title: Y2K Revival
description: Early 2000s fashion is making a major comeback with low-rise jeans, metallic fabrics, and chunky sneakers dominating the scene.

title: Sustainable Fashion
description: Eco-conscious fashion choices are trending with organic materials, upcycled clothing, and ethical brand partnerships leading the way.

title: Maximalist Prints
description: Bold, vibrant patterns are taking over with animal prints, geometric designs, and color-blocking creating statement looks.

title: Gender-Neutral Fashion
description: Breaking traditional boundaries with unisex designs, neutral colors, and inclusive sizing for all body types.

title: Tech-Wear Integration
description: Fashion meets technology with smart fabrics, wearable devices, and futuristic designs leading the innovation.

title: Cottagecore Aesthetic
description: Romantic, rural-inspired fashion with flowing dresses, floral prints, and vintage-style accessories.

title: Minimalist Wardrobe
description: Less is more approach with capsule wardrobes, neutral tones, and versatile pieces that mix and match effortlessly.

title: Vintage Denim
description: Classic denim styles from the 70s and 80s are resurging with high-waisted jeans, denim jackets, and vintage washes.

title: Athleisure Evolution
description: Athletic wear continues to evolve with luxury sportswear, performance fabrics, and seamless day-to-night transitions.
